from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler
def standardize_int_columns(data):
    int_columns = df1.select_dtypes(['int64']).columns
    sd = StandardScaler()
    for col in int_columns:
        data[col] = sd.fit_transform(data[col].values.reshape(-1,1))
    return data
